The '''Cactus Fruit''' is found via [[foraging]] in [[The Desert|the Calico Desert]]. It can also be bought at the [[Oasis]] on Tuesdays for {{price|150}} or randomly at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|75}}.

Cactus Fruit may also be grown from [[Cactus Seeds]].  Cactus Fruit grown from Cactus Seeds benefits from the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Tiller Profession]] bonus.

