==Bundles==
*Cactus Fruit is one of the options for the {{Bundle|Exotic Foraging||y}}.
*Cactus Fruit may be an option for the {{Bundle|Dye Remixed||y}}.

==Recipes==
Cactus Fruit is not used in any recipes.

==Buildings==
Cactus Fruit is used to construct [[Desert Obelisk]]s purchased from the [[Wizard's Tower]].

